</a></th><td colspan="2">24</td><td colspan="1" style="padding:0.2em 0.4em">September&#160;27,&#160;1985<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1985-09-27</span>)</span></td><td style="padding:0 8px">April&#160;11,&#160;1986<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="dtend">1986-04-11</span>)</span></td><td><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Aidman" title="Charles Aidman">Charles Aidman</a></td></tr><tr><td style="background:#EEE8AA;width:10px"></td><th scope="row" colspan="1" style="text-align:center"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_The_Twilight_Zone_(1985_TV_series)_episodes#Season_2_(1986–87)" title="List of The Twilight Zone (1985 TV series) episodes">7</a></th><td colspan="2">11</td><td colspan="1" style="padding:0.2em 0.4em">September&#160;27,&#160;1986<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1986-09-27</span>)</span></td><td style="padding:0 8px">July&#160;17,&#160;1987<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="dtend">1987-07-17</span>)</span></td><td>Charles Aidman</td></tr><tr><td style="background:#DA70D6;width:10px"></td><th scope="row" colspan="1" style="text-align:center"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_The_Twilight_Zone_(1985_TV_series)_episodes#Season_3_(1988–89)" title="List of The Twilight Zone (1985 TV series) episodes">8</a></th><td colspan="2">30</td><td colspan="1" style="padding:0.2em 0.4em">September&#160;24,&#160;1988<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1988-09-24</span>)</span></td><td style="padding:0 8px">April&#160;15,&#160;1989<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="dtend">1989-04-15</span>)</span></td><td rowspan="1"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Broadcast_syndication" title="Broadcast syndication">Syndication</a></td><td><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Ward_(television_personality)" title="Robin Ward (television personality)">Robin Ward</a></td></